      "description": "This 2018 Toyota 4Runner SR5 Premium offers a perfect blend of rugged capability and refined daily drivability. The Midnight Black Metallic exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical of a well-loved vehicle. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the heated SofTex seats show only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. Every electronic component, from the power moonroof to the touchscreen navigation and backup camera, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the 4.0L V6 runs smooth and quiet, backed by a comprehensive service history showing oil changes every 5,000 miles. We recently performed a full brake service and installed a fresh set of tires, ensuring this SUV is road-trip ready. The 4WD system shifts seamlessly, providing confidence in all weather conditions. While there are very faint surface scratches near the door handles from regular use, the overall presentation is professional and well-maintained. This is a reliable, honest vehicle that has been cared for with longevity in mind.",
